title: Dan Patrick - Hour 2 - NFL Insider Bucky Brooks
itunes:title: Dan Patrick - Hour 2 - NFL Insider Bucky Brooks
description:
In hour 2 on the Dan Patrick Show, Jason Smith and Mike Harmon start by talking about the NBA MVP award’s impact on players vying for the title, and draw a parallel to what the MVP in the NFL means to players. NFL veteran and insider Bucky Brooks joins the show to share some insight on Terrell Owens’ football comeback, Baker Mayfield’s whirlwind offseason, and more!
